49
00:03:09,370 --> 00:03:13,010
<i>It would be best if we don't have to battle Xiaoyu Yaoyao in the first round.</i>

50
00:03:14,740 --> 00:03:17,200
<i>It's almost time. Let's enter the arena.</i>

51
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:18,680
