80
00:05:47,150 --> 00:05:50,810
She turned over the command of the guild to Zhan Tianxia.

81
00:05:51,310 --> 00:05:54,760
Weiwei, I didn't realize I'd run into you.

82
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:57,020
Such a coincidence.

83
00:05:57,020 --> 00:05:59,520
Diemeng, you've returned.

84
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:01,450
Yes, I'm back.

85
00:06:01,450 --> 00:06:04,630
It's such a lively competition. Of course, I must be here.

86
00:06:05,410 --> 00:06:09,300
The second match of the points game now officially starts.

87
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:32,350
In the second match of the points game, Yixiao Naihe and

88
00:06:32,350 --> 00:06:36,270
Luwei Weiwei win in a complete victory, receiving three points.

89
00:06:45,270 --> 00:06:48,180
Weiwei, do you have time to chat?

90
00:06:49,380 --> 00:06:50,920
Okay.

91
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:03,530
<i>Do you still remember that we met here?</i>

92
00:07:03,530 --> 00:07:07,910
<i>At that time, I had a quest to kill an elite monster, but I couldn't defeat him.</i>

93
00:07:07,910 --> 00:07:09,810
<i>I was going to die once again.</i>

94
00:07:09,810 --> 00:07:13,320
<i>You suddenly dropped out of the sky and joined my group.</i>

95
00:07:14,190 --> 00:07:18,260
<i>At that time, I also needed to complete my mission.</i>

96
00:07:18,820 --> 00:07:23,870
<i>Back then, everyone was so happy, leveling up everyday, going to dungeons and discovering new territories.</i>

97
00:07:27,910 --> 00:07:30,750
<i>I fully understand what happened last time,</i>

98
00:07:30,750 --> 00:07:32,490
<i>and I scolded Tianxia.</i>

99
00:07:32,490 --> 00:07:35,910
<i>However, I still need to apologize to you.</i>

100
00:07:37,090 --> 00:07:41,730
<i>Diemeng, that thing doesn't concern you. You don't have to apologize to me.</i>

101
00:07:41,730 --> 00:07:43,490
<i>How could it not concern me?</i>

102
00:07:43,490 --> 00:07:47,150
<i>After all, I was the one who turned over the guild to Tianxia.</i>

103
00:07:47,150 --> 00:07:48,750
<i>I'm back now.</i>

104
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:51,850
<i>Weiwei, join the guild again. Okay?</i>

105
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:55,480
<i>I have a lot of exams coming up.</i>

106
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:58,130
<i>I don't want to use up too much energy playing games.</i>

107
00:07:58,130 --> 00:08:02,350
<i>I just decided to take part in the Couple's PK Competition but forget about the rest.</i>

108
00:08:09,590 --> 00:08:13,470
<i>Regarding certain matter, I heard that...</i>

109
00:08:15,170 --> 00:08:17,610
<i>Are you talking about Xiaoyu Qingqing?</i>

110
00:08:18,500 --> 00:08:20,930
<i>You knew?</i>

111
00:08:20,930 --> 00:08:24,050
<i>Of course. Don't worry. I'll take care of her.</i>

112
00:08:24,050 --> 00:08:27,330
<i>She won't be able to undermine my relationship with Tianxia.</i>

113
00:08:27,330 --> 00:08:31,710
<i>I never told you, but in the real world, we are actually a couple.</i>

114
00:08:31,710 --> 00:08:34,960
<i>Otherwise, why would I turn the guild over to him?</i>

115
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:40,890
<i>I see. That's good.</i>

116
00:08:46,530 --> 00:08:49,350
<i>In the blink of an eye, June is here already.</i>

117
00:08:49,350 --> 00:08:53,450
<i>Soon, our seniors will be leaving the school.</i>

118
00:08:53,450 --> 00:08:56,610
<i>They'll rush on to their next journey.</i>

