129
00:09:36,370 --> 00:09:39,280
Yes.

130
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:44,150
<i>Why haven't Diemeng Weixing and Zhan Tianxia shown up yet?</i>

131
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:46,380
