136
00:09:58,430 --> 00:10:00,040
<i>It can't be.</i>

137
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:02,170
<i>You can lose the game but not your reputation.</i>

138
00:10:02,170 --> 00:10:04,910
<i>Exactly.</i>

139
00:10:04,910 --> 00:10:09,110
