179
00:13:17,170 --> 00:13:20,920
<i>Weiwei, tomorrow I have a business dinner. I may come a little later.</i>

180
00:13:20,920 --> 00:13:22,790
<i>Okay. Then I'll come a little later, too.</i>

181
00:13:22,790 --> 00:13:24,270
<i>7:30 p.m. at the latest.</i>

182
00:13:24,270 --> 00:13:25,880
<i>Okay.</i>

183
00:13:26,410 --> 00:13:28,910
