184
00:13:31,030 --> 00:13:33,420
<i>Hello? Shaoxiang,</i>

185
00:13:33,420 --> 00:13:37,510
<i>Qingqing is complaining about us again; about how we didn't fight against Luwei Weiwei and Yixiao Naihe.</i>

186
00:13:37,510 --> 00:13:41,540
<i>Now, they've already become the server champions and are participating in the grand final.</i>

187
00:13:41,540 --> 00:13:43,840
