210
00:15:04,160 --> 00:15:09,260
<i>You, you. When will you mature a little?</i>

211
00:15:09,260 --> 00:15:13,170
<i>You've been in the office for a few days now. Have you settled in?</i>

212
00:15:13,170 --> 00:15:15,850
