214
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:22,070
<i>Didn't I already tell you very clearly?</i>

215
00:15:22,070 --> 00:15:24,980
<i>In the past, I let you play as you pleased.</i>

216
00:15:24,980 --> 00:15:29,370
<i>Now, it's time to become more focused to learn how to manage a company.</i>

217
00:15:29,370 --> 00:15:33,410
